========
dotfiles
========

this repository contains all my dotfiles. maintained with gnu stow.

init.sh script
==============

stows the following
 - bash
 - git
 - vscode
 - vim

does not stow the following
  - init
  - xfce-terminal

vscode keybindings
==================

- ctrl + shift + alt         modification
  - yuio     [editor group]  move non-cursor element around
  - hjkl     [editor]        move non-cursor element around
  - nm,.     [panel]         move non-cursor element around (sometimes buggy?)
  - p, /, c  [window]        create / delete / resize relative to whole window

- ctrl + alt                 navigation
  - yuio     [editor group]  move cursor highlight
  - hjkl     [editor]        move cursor highlight
  - nm,.     [panel]         move cursor highlight

- alt + shift                dialogs 
  - a        [window]        open file picker dialog
  - s        [window]        open editor dialog

- ctrl + shift   

- alt                        manipulation within a context
  - j        [context]       move down
  - k        [context]       move up
